    <item>
      <title>特朗普暂停大多数关税后，交易者对美联储削减的押注押注</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-09/short-term-treasuries-plunge-as-trump-pauses-most-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）暂停了对大多数国家的关税计划之后，交易者撤回了对今年美联储对削减税率的期望，而美国国债则跌落了两年。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-09/short-term-treasuries-plunge-as-trump-pauses-most-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 09 Apr 2025 17:59:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>高盛（Goldman Sachs）明年有65％的美国经济衰退机会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-09/goldman-sachs-sees-65-chance-of-us-recession-in-next-12-months</link>
      <description><![CDATA[高盛集团公司（Goldman Sachs Group Inc.）的经济学家说，他们现在在未来12个月内看到美国衰退的机会有65％，理由是唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统对美国贸易伙伴的关税。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-09/goldman-sachs-sees-65-chance-of-us-recession-in-next-12-months</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 09 Apr 2025 17:49:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
